This module allows you to fill in keywords on your pages to simplify finding
them afterwards.

**Table of contents**

.. contents::
   :local:

Installation
============

This module depends on module knowledge. So make sure to have it in your addons list.

Configuration
=============

No configuration required.

Usage
=====

Fill in your keywords, and search for them by typing (part of) the keyword and
choose searching for keywords.

Bug Tracker
===========

Bugs are tracked on `GitHub Issues <https://github.com/OCA/knowledge/issues>`_.
In case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.
If you spotted it first, help us smashing it by providing a detailed and welcomed
`feedback <https://github.com/OCA/knowledge/issues/new?body=module:%20document_page_tag%0Aversion:%2013.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**>`_.

Do not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.
